      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is a way that we can know the Life of Jesus;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And by this life we’ll be built up as one for His home;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just turn to Him and take His Word by prayer,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In your spirit daily pray His Word, pray His Word."
            }
